'''阿約塞·佩雷斯'''（{{lang-es|Ayoze Pérez}}；{{bd|1993年|7月23日}}）是一位[[西班牙|西班牙]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是前鋒。他現在效力於[[英格蘭足球超級聯賽|英格蘭足球超級聯賽]]球隊[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城足球俱乐部]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Starforth|first1=Miles|title=Ayoze Perez snubbed Barcelona AND Real Madrid to sign for Newcastle|url=http://www.shieldsgazette.com/sport/football/newcastle-united/ayoze-perez-snubbed-barcelona-and-real-madrid-to-sign-for-newcastle-1-6918975|accessdate=2014-10-27|newspaper=[[Shields_Gazette|Shields Gazette]]|date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170912055319/http://www.shieldsgazette.com/sport/football/newcastle-united/ayoze-perez-snubbed-barcelona-and-real-madrid-to-sign-for-newcastle-1-6918975|archive-date=2017-09-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Internacional/inglaterra/interior.aspx?content_id=887095|title=Newcastle contrata Ayoze Pérez|trans_title=Newcastle signs Ayoze Pérez|publisher=[[Record_(newspaper)|Record]]|language=pt|date=2014-06-05|accessdate=2014-06-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140606223356/http://www.record.xl.pt/Futebol/Internacional/inglaterra/interior.aspx?content_id=887095|archivedate=2014年6月6日}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/2014/05/21/futbol/equipos/tenerife/1400685788.html|title=Ayoze Pérez, al Newcastle|trans_title=Ayoze Pérez, to Newcastle|publisher=Marca|language=es|date=2014-05-21|accessdate=2014-06-06}}</ref>，之前效力过[[特內里費體育會|特内里费]]和[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]。他亦曾代表西班牙U21國家隊參賽<ref>{{cite web|last1=King|first1=Dan|title=Ayoze's Spanish Selection|url=http://www.nufc.co.uk/articles/20140829/ayozes-spanish-selection_2281670_4107385|publisher=Newcastle United F.C.|accessdate=2014-08-29|date=2014-08-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Watson-Broughton|first1=Matthew|title=Ñíguez fires Spain to Hungary success|url=http://www.uefa.com/under21/season=2015/matches/round=2000412/match=2011457/postmatch/report/index.html|publisher=UEFA|accessdate=2014-09-04|date=2014-09-04}}</ref>。

